These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, lemon, potato, cranberry
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, nigerian, british, argentine
1. the nigerian is on the left of the brazilian##1
2. the person eating peas is the argentine##1
3. the british is on the right of the brazilian##1
4. the person eating lemon is on the left of the argentine##1
5. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | cranberry | potato | lemon | peas   |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | brazilian     | british   | argentine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, hiking, photography, board-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, rowing, baseball, sailing
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | photography | board-games | hiking | traveling    |
| Sport   | baseball    | rowing      | tennis | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, puzzles, card-games, singing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, martial-arts, thriller, adventure
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | dancing | singing | card-games   | puzzles |
| Movie-Genre   | animation   | thriller | adventure | martial-arts         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, adventure, superhero, sports
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, handball, volleyball, swimming
1. the person who's sport is handball is the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | adventure | comedy  | superhero      |
| Sport         | handball | swimming   | volleyball | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, pear, potato, apple
4 different pets are kept: lizard, goat, frog, rabbit
1. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating banana##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person eating potato##1
3. the person eating apple is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | apple | potato | pear | banana |
| Pet    | lizard       | rabbit | frog | goat     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: british, indian, french, german
4 different pets are kept: ferret, turtle, guinea-pig, goat
1. the indian is on the far right##1
2. the german is on the left of the french##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the french##1
5. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | german | french | british | indian |
| Pet           | ferret      | guinea-pig | goat | turtle    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, reggae, hip-hop, jazz
4 different pets are kept: horse, guinea-pig, turtle, bird
1. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
5. the fan of reggae is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | reggae | punk | jazz  |
| Pet           | turtle | horse | bird       | guinea-pig |

