.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, social-worker, journalist, electrician
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, airplane, skateboard, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the social-worker##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is the electrician##1
3. the social-worker is on the right of the manager##1
4. the journalist is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | journalist | manager      | social-worker | electrician |
| Transport   | bike          | airplane | skateboard     | snowmobile    |

