.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, action, crime, documentary
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, snowmobile, bike, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | crime       | thriller | documentary   |
| Transport     | snowmobile | bike | quad-bike   | scooter |

