.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, water, lemonade
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, ship, helicopter, bike
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | iced-tea | water  | juice | lemonade |
| Transport   | bike | helicopter | ship          | snowmobile    |

