.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, coffee, juice, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, salsa, dubstep, trance
1. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
2. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking coffee is the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | juice | coffee  | cola | almond-milk |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | dubstep | trance           | salsa   |

