3. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the horse##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | lemonade | hot-chocolate  | milk | iced-tea   |
| Pet        | horse | cat | bird    | fish |

