.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, brazilian, colombian, german
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, tram, jet-ski, motorbike
1. the person driving the ship is on the left of the brazilian##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the left of the german##1
3. the australian is on the left of the colombian##1
4. the german is the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the ship is on the left of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | australian | colombian | brazilian | german   |
| Transport     | jet-ski  | ship    | tram       | motorbike |

 